{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/SVG","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>可縮放向量圖形</strong>（<em>Scalable Vector Graphics, SVG</em>）是基於 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XML\">XML <small>(en-US)</small></a> 語法的 2D 向量圖片格式。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C</a> 在 1990 晚期啟動 SVG 開發，但它要在 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Microsoft_Internet_Explorer\">IE <small>(en-US)</small></a> 9 開始支援 SVG 後才開始發跡。目前所有主流<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Browser\">瀏覽器</a>都支援 SVG。</p>\n<p>由於 SVG 基於 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XML\">XML <small>(en-US)</small></a> 語法，所以它可以透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a> 樣式化、並透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 互動。HTML5 目前能在 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> 檔案內直接嵌入 SVG <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Tag\">標籤 <small>(en-US)</small></a>。</p>\n<p>由於 SVG 是<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%9F%A2%E9%87%8F%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">向量圖形</a>，它因此可以無限縮放。也由於你可以建立介面元素（interface element）還有在任何螢幕尺寸縮放的圖形，它在<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Responsive_web_design\">響應式設計 <small>(en-US)</small></a>上也相當重要。SVG 也提供一組有用的工具，例如剪輯、遮罩、濾器、動畫（clipping, masking, filters, animation）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/SVG\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"理解_svg","title":"理解 SVG","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/IG/resources/svgprimer.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3.org 的 SVG Primer</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術資訊","title":"技術資訊","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG\">MDN 的 SVG 文件</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">最新的 SVG 規範</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"可縮放向量圖形（Scalable Vector Graphics, SVG）是基於 XML (en-US) 語法的 2D 向量圖片格式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"가변 벡터 도형 (SVG)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"SVG","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/svg","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/svg/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/SVG","title":"SVG"}],"pageTitle":"SVG - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}